description.plain:
Jason Andrè Juami (born January 27, 1997), better known by his stage name JAY1, is a British rapper and songwriter based on Coventry. He is of Congolese ancestry. He has had two singles that reached the top 20 list in the UK Official Charts.

JAY1 is best known for his single “Your Mrs”, which was released in March 2019. He released his debut EP titled One Wave on July 4, 2019.
